hopobject.body: Would you like to leave a message? hi mirror video In the following six months, I worked fast, sourcing a steel supplier from Cambridge, a leather factory from Manchester, injection-moulded plastics from Hampshire and adhesives from Preston. Using cutting-edge British manufacturing techniques we have improved quality, reduced waste by 20 per cent, cut six months from our pre-production phase and, most importantly, kept prices competitive with China.
